{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a66873d8e2","title":"视察黄河时的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"462598031d","index":0,"year":1952,"month":10,"day":29,"articleId":"a66873d8e2"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949.10-1957.12）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd.pdf"},{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"baa7bbe230","type":"paragraph","text":"老百姓拥护共产党，是因为我们代表了民族与人民的要求，但是如果我何不能解决经济间题，如果我们不能建立新式工业，如果我们不能发展生产力，老百姓就-定不拥护我何。","index":0,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"5c0462ea22","type":"paragraph","text":"如果我们共产党员不关心工业，不关心济，也不得到别的什工有益的工作，对这一些-一无所知，一无所能，只会作一种抽象的“革命工作”，这种重命家是毫无价航的，我们应蔽反对这些尘头革命家，学习使中国工业化的各种技术知。","index":1,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"2926508ef0","type":"paragraph","text":"博引自李先念：《努力学好经济工作》","index":2,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"76ff9e2f88","type":"paragraph","text":"（《人民日报》一九五二年七月十四日）","index":3,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"27f001d357","type":"paragraph","text":"封信给、李×的","index":4,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"5b66f1bcac","type":"paragraph","text":"××克：","index":5,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"8350b804e4","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十一日的信收到。以前儿也都收到了。爱晚亭三字已照写如另瓶。","index":6,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"68f28514f5","type":"paragraph","text":"矛盾融第四章第十段第三行“无融什么矛盾，也无融在什么时候矛盾着的方面，其发展是不平衡的。”这里“也无在什工时”八字应删，在选集第-卷第二版时，已将这八字去。你写解时，请加注意为盼！","index":7,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"890bb552df","type":"paragraph","text":"顺候敬安","index":8,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"e666e32fec","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":9,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"0a47276859","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五二年九月十七日视察黄河时的谈话","index":10,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"4e55506e95","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五二年十月二十九日）老根据地的人民出了大力，我何要注意帮助他们。","index":11,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"a71ba484ea","type":"paragraph","text":"这个大水康（三门峡）修起来，把几千年以来的黄河水患解决啦，还能灌溉平原的农田几千万亩，发电一百万迁，通行输船也有了条件，是可以研究的。","index":12,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"aa505a5cce","type":"paragraph","text":"南方水多，北方水少，如有可能，借一点水来是可以的。","index":13,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"1a3074e93d","type":"paragraph","text":"对民建方针指示的精神","index":14,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"508c43fae9","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五二年）、私人看本在中国建设上是有查献的，只要不额它向坏的方面发展。","index":15,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"a66873d8e2"}],"page":{"id":"42d97bf930","publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"a66873d8e2","start":31,"end":31}},"maoquanji32":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"146e28e07d","type":"paragraph","text":"一九二至十日三十闭","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"6bf6550eb4","type":"subtitle","text":"要批发场级手佳资好无汉东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"6c65ae2a44","type":"title","text":"视察黄河时的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"8e89c89e82","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东题写的“要把黄河的事情办好”","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"ab26cf14b5","type":"paragraph","text":"老根据地的人民出了大力，我们要注意帮助他们","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"af33ce8917","type":"paragraph","text":"南方水多，北方水少，如有可能，借一点水来是可以的。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a66873d8e2"},{"id":"c19d6da45c","type":"paragraph","text":"这个大水库（三门峡）修起来，把几千年以来的黄河水患解决啦，还能灌溉平原的农田几千万亩，发电一百万千瓦，通行轮船也有了条件，是可以研究的。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a66873d8e2"}],"page":{"id":"c4550c04bc","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"a66873d8e2","start":320,"end":320}}}},"__N_SSG":true}